AstroGPT: A GenAI Model for Simplifying Astrophysics Research

AstroGPT is a GenAI system fine-tuned from GPT-2 that rewrites complex astrophysics research abstractsâ€”sourced directly from arXivâ€”into clear, engaging explanations for a general audience.
The project includes automated data ingestion, teacher-prompt generation, simplification pipelines, and model fine-tuning, all built to operate end-to-end from Python.

